data.description: This brick ranch home  ready to move in for a large foamily offers three bedrooms,1.1/2 full bath and  two cars attached garage with the opener it sits  on a corner lot.  Also, finished basement offers extra two bedrooms and another sitting room,  and perfect size kitchen. Newly updated with fresh paint, new flooring, and a modernized full bath, the home also offers sizable bedrooms and a heated family room. The backyard includes a patio with direct access from the family room. Home come with all appliances,   seller provide C of O at closing. All measurements are approximate. BATVAI
